                        <span class="tag">cuDNN</span>
                        <span class="tag">cuBLAS</span>
                        <span class="tag">cuFFT</span>
                        <span class="tag">NCCL</span>
                        <span class="tag">TensorRT</span>
                        <span class="tag">TransformerEngine</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="layer layer-runtime">
                    <div class="layer-header">
                        <span class="layer-icon">⚙️</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">CUDA 运行时与工具</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-desc">CUDA 程序的开发、编译和运行环境</div>
                    <div class="layer-items">
                        <span class="tag">CUDA Toolkit</span>
                        <span class="tag">CUDA Runtime</span>
                        <span class="tag">nvcc 编译器</span>
                        <span class="tag">CUDA Driver API</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="layer layer-driver">
                    <div class="layer-header">
                        <span class="layer-icon">🔌</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">驱动层</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-desc">操作系统与 GPU 硬件的桥梁，负责资源管理和任务调度</div>
                    <div class="layer-items">
                        <span class="tag">NVIDIA Driver</span>
                        <span class="tag">NVIDIA Container Toolkit</span>
                        <span class="tag">nvidia-smi</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="layer layer-hardware">
                    <div class="layer-header">
                        <span class="layer-icon">🖥️</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">硬件层</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-desc">物理 GPU 设备，执行实际的并行计算</div>
                    <div class="layer-items">
                        <span class="tag">A100 / H100</span>
                        <span class="tag">RTX 4090</span>
                        <span class="tag">Jetson Orin</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 详细工具卡片 -->
        <section class="cards-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">📦 核心组件详解</h2>
            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Hardware Interface</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">🔌</div>
                        <div class="card-title">NVIDIA Driver</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>操作系统与 GPU 的桥梁。管理 GPU 硬件资源、内存分配、任务调度。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>这是唯一必须安装在<strong>宿主机</strong>上的组件。所有 CUDA 程序都通过驱动与 GPU 通信。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">宿主机安装</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag green">必须</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Container Support</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">🐳</div>
                        <div class="card-title">NVIDIA Container Toolkit</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>让 Docker 容器能够访问宿主机的 GPU。将驱动文件和 GPU 设备映射进容器。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>安装后在 Docker 中可以使用 <code>--gpus all</code> 参数。宿主机安装即可，容器内不需要。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">宿主机安装</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">docker --gpus</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Development Platform</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">⚙️</div>
                        <div class="card-title">CUDA Toolkit</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>完整的 CUDA 开发环境。包含编译器(nvcc)、运行时库、调试工具、数学库等。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>通常安装在<strong>容器内</strong>，与宿主机驱动解耦。不同项目可用不同 CUDA 版本。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">容器内安装</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag green">nvcc</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">开发必备</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Runtime Only</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">▶️</div>
                        <div class="card-title">CUDA Runtime</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>CUDA 程序运行所需的最低环境，不含编译工具。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>如果你只运行预编译好的 CUDA 程序（如 PyTorch 二进制包），只需要 Runtime，不需要完整 Toolkit。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">体积更小</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">运行即可</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Deep Learning Primitives</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">🚀</div>
                        <div class="card-title">cuDNN</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>CUDA Deep Neural Network library。针对深度学习优化的 GPU 加速原语（卷积、RNN、注意力等）。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>PyTorch/TensorFlow 底层调用 cuDNN 实现 GPU 加速。必须与 CUDA 版本严格匹配。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">框架依赖</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag green">版本敏感</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Linear Algebra</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">🔢</div>
                        <div class="card-title">cuBLAS / cuFFT / cuRAND</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>CUDA 基础数学库。cuBLAS（线性代数）、cuFFT（快速傅里叶变换）、cuRAND（随机数生成）。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>PyTorch 的矩阵运算、TensorFlow 的卷积底层都依赖这些库。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">CUDA Toolkit 包含</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">基础数学</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Multi-GPU Communication</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">🔗</div>
                        <div class="card-title">NCCL</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>NVIDIA Collective Communications Library。多 GPU / 多节点间的集合通信（AllReduce、Broadcast 等）。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>分布式训练（DDP、DeepSpeed、Horovod）的核心依赖。支持 NVLink 和 InfiniBand 高速互联。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">分布式训练</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag green">多卡必备</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">Inference Optimization</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
                        <div class="card-title">TensorRT</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>推理优化引擎。通过层融合、精度校准（FP16/INT8）、内核自动调优，最大化推理性能。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>仅用于<strong>推理阶段</strong>，不用于训练。可将模型延迟降低 10-100 倍。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">推理专用</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag green">性能优化</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-subtitle">LLM Training</div>
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <div class="card-icon">🤖</div>
                        <div class="card-title">TransformerEngine</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <strong>作用：</strong>NVIDIA 专为 Transformer 模型设计的加速库。提供 FP8 训练、FlashAttention 集成等。<br><br>
                        <strong>关键：</strong>大语言模型（LLM）训练的重要加速组件，集成在最新 NGC PyTorch 镜像中。
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-meta">
                        <span class="meta-tag">LLM 专用</span>
                        <span class="meta-tag">FP8</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 依赖关系 -->
        <section class="relationship">
            <h2 class="section-title">🔗 依赖关系链</h2>
            <div class="rel-diagram">
                <div class="rel-box">
                    <h3>1. NVIDIA Driver（宿主机）</h3>
                    <p>必须最先安装。决定系统支持的最高 CUDA 版本。用 <code>nvidia-smi</code> 查看驱动版本和 GPU 状态。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rel-arrow"><span>⬇️</span></div>
                <div class="rel-box">
                    <h3>2. NVIDIA Container Toolkit（宿主机）</h3>
                    <p>可选但强烈建议。让 Docker 容器能使用 GPU。安装后 <code>docker run --gpus all</code> 即可。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rel-arrow"><span>⬇️</span></div>
                <div class="rel-box">
                    <h3>3. CUDA Toolkit（容器内）</h3>
                    <p>版本 ≤ 宿主机驱动支持的最高版本。包含 Runtime + 开发工具。不同容器可用不同版本。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rel-arrow"><span>⬇️</span></div>
                <div class="rel-box">
                    <h3>4. cuDNN / NCCL / 其他库（容器内）</h3>
                    <p>必须与 CUDA Toolkit 版本匹配。通常由框架自动依赖，或打包在 NGC 镜像中。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="rel-arrow"><span>⬇️</span></div>
                <div class="rel-box">
                    <h3>5. PyTorch / TensorFlow（容器内）</h3>
                    <p>框架版本决定所需的 CUDA/cuDNN 版本。如 PyTorch 2.3 需要 CUDA 12.1 + cuDNN 8.9。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 容器化对比 -->
        <section class="container-comparison">
            <h2 class="section-title">🐳 宿主机 vs 容器化安装对比</h2>
            <table class="comparison-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>组件</th>
                        <th>宿主机安装</th>
                        <th>容器内安装</th>
                        <th>说明</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>NVIDIA Driver</strong></td>
                        <td>✅ 必须</td>
                        <td>❌ 不需要</td>
                        <td>唯一必须装在宿主机的组件</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>NVIDIA Container Toolkit</strong></td>
                        <td>✅ 需要</td>
                        <td>❌ 不需要</td>
                        <td>让 Docker 能访问 GPU</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>CUDA Toolkit</strong></td>
                        <td>⚪ 可选</td>
                        <td>✅ 推荐</td>
                        <td>容器化可实现多版本共存</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>cuDNN</strong></td>
                        <td>⚪ 可选</td>
                        <td>✅ 推荐</td>
                        <td>与 CUDA 版本严格绑定</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>PyTorch/TensorFlow</strong></td>
                        <td>⚪ 可选</td>
                        <td>✅ 推荐</td>
                        <td>框架版本与 CUDA 版本需匹配</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </section>

        <!-- 安装命令 -->
        <section class="install-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">🛠️ 快速安装参考</h2>
            <div class="install-grid">
                <div class="install-card">
                    <h3>宿主机：安装驱动 + Container Toolkit</h3>
                    <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># Ubuntu 安装驱动（示例）</span>
<span class="command">sudo apt update</span>
<span class="command">sudo apt install nvidia-driver-535</span>

<span class="comment"># 安装 Container Toolkit</span>
<span class="command">sudo apt install nvidia-container-toolkit</span>
<span class="command">sudo nvidia-ctk runtime configure --runtime=docker</span>
<span class="command">sudo systemctl restart docker</span>

<span class="comment"># 验证</span>
<span class="command">nvidia-smi</span>
<span class="command">docker run --rm --gpus all nvidia/cuda:12.1.0-base-ubuntu22.04 nvidia-smi</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="install-card">
                    <h3>容器：使用 NGC 镜像（推荐）</h3>
                    <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 拉取预配置好的 PyTorch 环境</span>
<span class="command">docker pull nvcr.io/nvidia/pytorch:26.04-py3</span>

<span class="comment"># 运行并挂载代码和数据</span>
<span class="command">docker run --gpus all -it --rm \</span>
<span class="command">  -v $(pwd)/project:/workspace \</span>
<span class="command">  -v /data:/data \</span>
<span class="command">  nvcr.io/nvidia/pytorch:26.04-py3 \</span>
<span class="command">  bash</span>

<span class="comment"># 容器内已包含：CUDA 12.x + cuDNN + PyTorch + NCCL</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="install-card">
                    <h3>版本兼容性检查</h3>
                    <div class="code-block">
<span class="comment"># 查看驱动支持的最高 CUDA 版本</span>
<span class="command">nvidia-smi</span>
<span class="comment"># 右上角显示 CUDA Version: 12.4</span>

<span class="comment"># 查看 PyTorch 使用的 CUDA 版本</span>
<span class="command">python -c "import torch; print(torch.version.cuda)"</span>

<span class="comment"># 查看 cuDNN 版本</span>
<span class="command">python -c "import torch; print(torch.backends.cudnn.version())"</span>

<span class="comment"># 验证 GPU 是否可用</span>
<span class="command">python -c "import torch; print(torch.cuda.is_available())"</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>NVIDIA 深度学习工具全景图 | 基于 CUDA 12.x / NGC 2026 版本整理</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.85em;">建议始终参考 <a href="https://docs.nvidia.com" style="color: #76b900; text-decoration: none;">NVIDIA 官方文档</a> 获取最新信息</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // 简单的平滑滚动
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({
                    behavior: 'smooth'
                });
            });
        });

        // 卡片点击效果
        document.querySelectorAll('.card').forEach(card => {
            card.addEventListener('click', function() {
                this.style.transform = 'scale(0.98)';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    this.style.transform = '';
                }, 150);
            });
        });
    </script>
